data.description: Welcome to 24 Idolstone Rd! This spacious 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home is an absolute gem. As you walk up the driveway, you're greeted by a beautifully landscaped yard that sets the tone for what's inside. Stepping through the stylish entrance door, you enter a welcoming hallway.   To the left, a convenient half bathroom awaits, perfect for guests during gatherings. To the right, the main bedroom which features a spacious walk-in closet and a luxurious bathroom that's sure to impress. Moving forward, you'll discover a bright and airy living room adorned with large windows, flooding the space with natural light. The adjacent stunning kitchen boasts updated stainless steel appliances and a versatile island/breakfast bar, ideal for casual dining or entertaining. Adjacent to the kitchen, the dining area continues the theme of natural light streaming in through large windows.   Upstairs, a full bathroom serves three well-sized bedrooms, one of which boasts yet another walk-in closet. The convenience of a dedicated laundry room upstairs adds to the functionality of this home.   Outside, the yard is a haven for both relaxation and entertainment. Fully fenced for privacy, it features a swing set, a patio for al fresco dining, and a shed for storage, all surrounded by ample yard for various activities.   Conveniently located close to major highways and shopping centers, this home offers both comfort and accessibility. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home. Schedule your tour today!
